songs.title: Smile
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Boom...

Still can't seem to figure out
What happens in my head
The thought alone is gunna kill me
Sick of living with this doubt
This pistol in my hand
I could end it all before the morning
But summertime always gon' come around
How we, waiting for another smile
Lift my feet off the ground

Try to hold on, gravity won't let me go
This gravity won't let me go (go, go)
This gravity won't let me go

The devil always smile when you need a friend
I'm laying on this cloud
It's a long drive back to earth
Wonder where my happy days will fade away
Don't rain on my parade
If it's only for this moment
So gravity let me go

So can you please let me go?
Let me go
Oh, woah, woah
Will you let me get higher?
Higher
I just wanna get higher
Higher
Wanna get high
Said I wanna get higher
Said I wanna get higher
Let me get higher
I wanna get high
Said I wanna get high
(Yeah, yeah, yeah)

Gravity, can you let me go?
